definitions.definition: Any member of a Native American tribe formerly living along the Klamath River in California and Oregon .

main_definition: Any member of a Native American tribe formerly living along the Klamath River in California and Oregon .

definitions.definition: The language of this tribe (also known as Klamath- Modoc ).
A river in southern Oregon , and northern California .
A county in southern Oregon ; see Klamath County .
A former county in northern California .
A census-designated place in Del Norte County , California , United States .
